casebody.data:
No. 11-6616. Paul Blackmer, Petitioner v. Social Security Administration. 565 U.S. 1051, 132 S. Ct. 799,

181 L. Ed. 2d 476,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8445. November 28, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied, and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
